## A full-stack Human Resource Management System (HRMS) built using:

Frontend: React (Vite) + Axios

Backend: FastAPI + SQLAlchemy

Database: SQLite / PostgreSQL (via Render)

## Deployment:

Backend â†’ Render

Frontend â†’ Vercel

This project allows managing employees and daily attendance through a simple web interface.

